Ann Marie has been invited to be a feature artist at Amazing Things on 160 Hollis Street in Framingham on Wednesday, January 13th!
Cabaret Open Mike starts at 7:30pm, and my show is at 9pm sharp~!
Come sing, come watch, or come watch and sing!, it will be amazing! Come and beat the post holiday blues!

Go to the link below to purchase your ticket. They are $10 each.
